{"tid":511641,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"米奇老味神奇屋個奶油王痴撚咗線","createTime":"2017-12-27T16:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T17:11:22.000Z","uid":63603,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7be19779d3e781ecc18161025a18418a314568b","tid":511641,"uid":63603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"食屎啦，今晚場Show真係我睇Live咁耐最差既一次。<br />\n<br />\n就算頭2 part 係唔知做乜由其係個女Rapper 唔算好好，但都唔係叫人落台過主啦下話?睇Live既基本尊重都無，叫個班真係唔撚該過主，無資格繼續聽落去。<br />\n<br />\n成晚成班撚屌跟風友係咪都手碗裡邊住個煲，係咪都鳩叫，到唱舊歌個陣又無撚人識唱，由其龍城大藥房呢首成名作跟住唱既人分分鐘一半都無，大部份人大部份時間都成碌木咁，唔知以為去左兵馬俑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後就係中間班撚屌明知通風差仲狂食煙，又焗又臭，同一年前HA場SHOW既風氣真係天同地比，觀眾質素真係垃圾到阿媽都唔認得。"},{"pid":"7b6a53514bd0888f1286ef4fe8e1119be073a640","tid":511641,"uid":63603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"出錯野請無視"},{"pid":"891302b3893abca65bbc9787536f10920a3d0058","tid":511641,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:57:44.000Z","msg":"事實，講中晒<br />\n叫人走一d禮貌都冇<br />\n好多mk入去圍威喂<br />\n成場就係到煲煙<br />\n唔好話ha,同上次九展都差好遠<br />\n<br />\nBtw,個場勁垃圾，冇冷氣，個廁所兩個都壞既，仲核特過公廁，屌。下次呢個場搞真係唔撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ffcb432de2efaa10e841740ca288347ddf5a1b","tid":511641,"uid":149116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T17:00:26.000Z","msg":"個show都唔係for你地班毒撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a6edd0b17070bf8081a183a7a0c961207f75e7","tid":511641,"uid":63603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95ffcb432de2efaa10e841740ca288347ddf5a1b","tid":511641,"uid":149116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyT